    <step order="2">Author §6.x "Per-environment service-principal provisioning" subsection with: rationale (why 3 distinct SPs), exact `az ad sp create-for-rbac` commands per env, federated identity credential setup with `gh secret set` syntax, role assignment commands, verification.</step>
    <step order="3">Include the operator checklist: 3 GitHub Environment secrets named AZURE_CLIENT_ID_DEV / _STAGING / _PROD.</step>
